### Dual-verification attendance flow (student JWT required)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_STUDENT_JWT

### Step 1 — Verify face (returns faceVerificationToken, ~5 min TTL)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ml/verify-face
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "BASE64_JPEG_WITHOUT_PREFIX"
}

###

### Step 2 — Mark attendance (face token + live faculty QR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/student/mark-attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrToken": "FACULTY_LIVE_QR_TOKEN",
  "faceVerificationToken": "TOKEN_FROM_VERIFY_FACE"
}

###

### Deprecated — face-only (returns 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ml/recognize-face
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "BASE64",
  "sessionId": "SESSION_ID"
}
